data.description: New Interior Paint, New Carpet, Upgraded Lighting, Hardwoods On Main!  Rare Three Car Garage Home w/Rocking Chair Front Porch.  Formal Dining Room Leads To Open Concept Family Room.  Family Room w/Gas Fireplace w/TV Mount Above. Gourmet, Granite Kitchen w/White Cabinets, Custom Tile Backsplash, Giant Island w/Breakfast Bar & Pendant Lights, Stainless Appliances, Including Double Ovens, Built-In Microwave & Eat-In Breakfast Area.  Bedroom & Full Bath Complete The Main. Upstairs Features Loft/ Office Area. Primary Suite Has Trey Ceiling, Bath w/Tall Vanities, Separate Garden Tub & Shower & Access To Upstairs Laundry Room.  3 Additional Bedrooms Share Third Bath.  Flat, Backyard Fenced On 3 Sides!  Awesome Neighborhood Amenities Include Pool & Playground.  Check Out Rate Buy Down Option To Make This House Affordable!
